**Idea**
1.  We have three choices: Either we can choose first Pass, second Pass or Last Pass
2.  If any day is within validity of earlier choosen pass then we can travel without any cost.
3.  Base Condition: If we complete our travel, we don't need to pay any cost 

**Brute Force [Recursion]**
