# Intuition
- First of all we are at index 0 .
- Now we have 3 types of passes 1day ,7day,30day , and we have to choose that pass so that i can plan the whole trip at minimum possible price.
- So we make call at all the three options and return the value which is minimum from all those options.
- And when we are out of the array then no other days remaining so just return 0 cost .
# Approach
-Used memoization and return the minimum possible cost at each stage.
In second approach , i have made a solveTab function in which tabulation is done .

# Complexity
- Time complexity:
O(n^2) 

- Space complexity:
O(n) -> for the DP array to store the value at each stage and to prevent unneccessary subProblem calls which are already taken place.

# Code
