The idea is to record the max and min till current position. If the gap between min and max exceeds limit, left of window will move to min(position of min, position of max).

```
class Solution {
    public int longestSubarray(int[] nums, int limit) {
        int min = Integer.MAX_VALUE;
        int posmin = 0;
        int max = Integer.MIN_VALUE;
        int posmax = 0;
        int idx = 0;
        int left = 0;
        int res = 0;
        while (idx<nums.length){
            if (nums[idx]>max){
                max = nums[idx];
                posmax = idx;
            }
            if (nums[idx]<min){
                min = nums[idx];
                posmin = idx;
            }
            if (max-min<=limit){
                res = Math.max(res, idx-left+1);
                idx++;
            }else{
                left = Math.min(posmin, posmax)+1;
                idx = left;
                min = Integer.MAX_VALUE;
                max = Integer.MIN_VALUE;
            }
        }
        return res;
    }
}
